{"tid":1429064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線短期目標：逼美國政府/國會出聲明關注解放軍武警入侵","createTime":"2019-08-07T12:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T10:31:48.000Z","uid":294139,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bb452a3cd0b50f5100b936ab7d86f5421f335fd5","tid":1429064,"uid":294139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得純粹指責中共違反聯合聲明都係太虛，要比D更近期、更具體同更大逼切性嘅例子比美國做子彈先得，而懷疑解放軍/武警<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經</span></strong>混入警隊應該唔錯，因為中共曾經向美國承諾唔會派兵，但如果有證據令美國起質疑而出聲明問，咁樣<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可以進一步增加我地籌碼</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而剛好今日已經有國際媒體關注：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gauseee/photos/a.390139987771802/2280577235394725/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgauseee%2Fphotos%2Fa.390139987771802%2F2280577235394725%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=70563b93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gauseee/photos/a.390139987771802/2280577235394725/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n加埋呢段片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yUeKjVMQN_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyUeKjVMQN_0&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=b51724df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yUeKjVMQN_0</a><br />\n<br />\n只要我地再不斷收集類似證據，然後推至國際層面，令美國起疑，咁樣先可以更確立到香港情況危急，中共絕對有機會武力鎮壓，美國行動要更快"},{"pid":"d486640726060d4830ad36a9c6c86a1ce5ab3f8d","tid":1429064,"uid":287594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:01:33.000Z","msg":"借位推<br />\n<br />\n【文宣新方向】乜鬼野五大，七大訴求呀??<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429008</a>"},{"pid":"0dde0afd00319fbb2269d1f7e087e2e4fd441d8c","tid":1429064,"uid":259423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"P